detailedDescription.articleBody: The A5 is a 25-kilometre-long motorway, located in the Lisbon metropolitan area, Portugal. It connects Lisbon with Cascais. The motorway is also known as Estoril Coast Motorway and it overlaps the Complementary Itinerary 15.

detailedDescription.articleBody: The A5 motorway is a motorway in Croatia spanning 55.5 kilometres. It connects Osijek, the largest city in Slavonia region, to the Croatian motorway network at the Sredanci interchange of the A3 motorway.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: A5 मोटरवे क्रोएशिया में 55,5 किलोमीटर तक फैला एक मोटरवे है, यह स्लावोनिया क्षेत्र के सबसे बड़े शहर ओसिजेक को A3 मोटरवे के सेरेडांसी इंटरचेंज में क्रोएशियाई मोटरवे नेटवर्क से जोड़ता है।

detailedDescription.articleBody: Bundesautobahn 5 is a 445 km long Autobahn in Germany. Its northern end is the Hattenbach triangle intersection with the A 7. The southern end is at the Swiss border near Basel.

detailedDescription.articleBody: The Autostrada A5 is an Italian motorway, which connects Turin and the Aosta Valley to France, through the Mont Blanc Tunnel.
